Download the three font families below and place them here.
The HTML template loads them from Google Fonts CDN; local files are used when offline.

  DM Serif Display  — https://fonts.google.com/specimen/DM+Serif+Display
  Inter (weight 900) — https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Inter
  JetBrains Mono (400, 500) — https://fonts.google.com/specimen/JetBrains+Mono

Naming convention:  DMSerifDisplay-Regular.woff2
                    Inter-Black.woff2
                    JetBrainsMono-Regular.woff2
                    JetBrainsMono-Medium.woff2

After adding files, add @font-face rules to template.html pointing to
../../assets/fonts/<filename> and remove the Google Fonts <link> tag.
